# Wait for Explicit Instructions

**Never assume or start building** when the user has not explicitly asked for it.

- Do not implement features, add pages, or create new functionality unless the user clearly requests it
- If the user describes something (e.g. "the office will consist of..."), wait for them to ask you to build it
- Ask before implementing when intent is unclear
